                <mxCell id="legend" value="&lt;b&gt;One-hot FSM&lt;/b&gt; (6 states). Counters: row_cnt (weight rows), load_cnt (activation bits), bp_cnt (bit-planes).&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;Per-state outputs:&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;WRITE_W: w_en (on wfull), row_addr&lt;br&gt;WRITE_A: a_en; clr pulses on last bit (511)&lt;br&gt;COMPUTE: comp_en, a_en, bp_idx&lt;br&gt;DONE: y_load (capture result)&lt;br&gt;SHIFT_OUT: y_en (serial drain)&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;Green loop:&lt;/b&gt; weight-stationary — cont reuses loaded weights, skips WRITE_W." style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;align=left;verticalAlign=top;fillColor=#f5f5f5;strokeColor=#999999;fontSize=11;spacing=6;" parent="1" vertex="1">
